  "text": "Step (3) assembles the enumeration problem and validates it, so that in Step (4) the proper formulation is built and solved. MCSs that are not feasible in the desired space are discarded, leaving only cMCSs. Right brief overview of the MILP formulation. S ′ and v ′ are derived from the dual model formulation in [CITATION_1] which already includes the undesired phenotypes",
